Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在是朋友了吗？\N{\rEN}Are we friends now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.08,0:02:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 我从来没见过你 你好吗\N{\rEN}Hey, I haven't seen you in forever. How are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我很好 \N{\rEN}No, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪 他这么说？\N{\rEN}My gosh, he said that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.19,0:02:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊 太可爱了！\N{\rEN}My god, that is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊 太可爱了！\N{\rEN}My god, that is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.40,0:03:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天啊 太可爱了！\N{\rEN}My god, that is so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,, - 早上好！ - 你好 安吉拉阿姨 \N{\rEN}- Morning! - Hi, Aunt Angela.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,, - 给 让我来 我来了 - 谢谢 \N{\rEN}- Here, let me get it. I got it. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.80,0:03:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我看起来怎么样？我知道这才9个月 但我不知道 \N{\rEN}How do I look? I know it's only been nine months, but I don't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.15,0:03:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我觉得我好像少了一两步  - 你看起来很棒 \N{\rEN}- I feel like I lost a step or two. - You look great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,女士们早餐变冷了！\N{\rEN}Ladies! Breakfast is getting cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.59,0:03:19.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我闻到了碳水化合物的味道 为什么他总是这样？\N{\rEN}I smell carbs. Why does he always do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.96,0:03:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因为他在努力 因为我们就是这样做的 对吧？\N{\rEN}Because he's trying. Because that's what we do, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们站起来 让它发挥作用 \N{\rEN}We rise above and we make it work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,, - 米阿莫尔 王子  - 来了！\N{\rEN}- Mi amor. Princesa. - Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 以前简单多了 \N{\rEN}I mean, it was just so much simpler before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 是的 但我为你感到骄傲 \N{\rEN}I know. It was. But I'm proud of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我为我们感到骄傲 我是说 看看我们 我们是完整的 \N{\rEN}I'm proud of us. I mean, look at us. We're complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.40,0:03:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我们现在就像一个幸福的大家庭  - 减去碳水化合物 \N{\rEN}- We're like one big, happy family now. - Minus the carbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.87,0:03:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢那个 \N{\rEN}I like that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,下面见 \N{\rEN}See you down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不 太可爱了 \N{\rEN}No, that's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你想喝杯咖啡吗？ - 是的 请 \N{\rEN}- You want a coffee? - Yes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 漂亮 \N{\rEN}Hey, gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我爱你穿这些衣服  - 退出 \N{\rEN}- I love you in these. - Quit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.75,0:04:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能 \N{\rEN}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好烙饼？\N{\rEN}Good morning! Pancakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.12,0:04:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,今天是大日子吗？\N{\rEN}So, big day today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.72,0:04:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我们还有大约两周的时间  - 你紧张吗？\N{\rEN}- We're still about two weeks out. - You nervous?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛并不紧张 不像她的阿姨 \N{\rEN}Emma doesn't get nervous. Not like her auntie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她有这个 \N{\rEN}She's got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我们今天已经完成了舞蹈的学习 \N{\rEN}We actually finish learning the dance routine today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,它很短 就像四个八点计数 \N{\rEN}It's short, like, four eight counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,然后我们要发表演讲 向大家介绍 \N{\rEN}Then we have to make a speech, we present to everybody,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.12,0:04:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,然后每个人都投票 \N{\rEN}then everyone votes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,获奖者是舞蹈队少年队长 \N{\rEN}and the winner is Dance Team Captain Junior year.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,有竞争吗？\N{\rEN}Any competition?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芬 但是   \N{\rEN}Steph, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 不是真的 你知道吗？\N{\rEN}I mean, not really, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.68,0:04:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 Digame \N{\rEN}I don't know. Digame.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.36,0:04:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我有点棒 \N{\rEN}I'm kinda awesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,, - 恩español？ - 我学法语 \N{\rEN}- En español? - I take French.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Je suis géniale \N{\rEN}Je suis géniale.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,此外 你不是真正的古巴人 \N{\rEN}Besides, it's not like you're really Cuban.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.04,0:05:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大豆酱！我是说 当然 我只是一个巨大的古巴档案 \N{\rEN}Soy asombroso! I mean, sure, I'm just a huge Cuba-file,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.51,0:05:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但我身上可能有古巴血统 \N{\rEN}but there could be some Cuban blood in me somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在年底前让你说流利的 \N{\rEN}I'm going to get you fluent by the end of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芬的妈妈经营儿科 \N{\rEN}Steph's mom runs Pediatrics.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.68,0:05:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,瑞秋和我是多年的朋友 \N{\rEN}Rachel and I have been friends for years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 祝最好的舞者获胜 \N{\rEN}Well, may the best dancer win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.31,0:05:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,试试看 它们不含麸质 零卡路里 \N{\rEN}Try them. They're gluten-free. Zero-calorie.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,高蛋白 \N{\rEN}High-protein.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这么好 \N{\rEN}So good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.48,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEN}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.83,0:05:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你真有趣 米吉托！你真有趣！\N{\rEN}You are so funny, mijito! You are so funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不能比你爸爸聪明！不 你不能 \N{\rEN}But you can't outsmart your papa! No, you cannot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.31,0:05:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这些天他喜欢两件事 \N{\rEN}Two things he loves these days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.16,0:05:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,美味的燕麦和他的勺子 \N{\rEN}Yummy Oats and throwing his spoons.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.75,0:05:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,给你 \N{\rEN}There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,, - 嘿 你确定你没事吗？ - 好吗？你在开玩笑吧？\N{\rEN}- Hey, you sure you're okay with this? - Okay with it? Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.68,0:05:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我很幸运 \N{\rEN}I'm lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 远程课程更短了 我开始写书 \N{\rEN}I mean, remote classes are shorter, I get to work on my book,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,修复野兽 \N{\rEN}fix up The Beast.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.31,0:06:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我讨厌野兽  - 不 你喜欢野兽   \N{\rEN}- I hate The Beast. - No, you love The Beast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我会完善我的烹饪 最重要的是 \N{\rEN}And I get to perfect my cooking and, best of all,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我要照顾我们的儿子 \N{\rEN}I get to take care of our son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.19,0:06:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以在游泳池周围设置围栏\N{\rEN}And you get to put up a fence around the pool
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.36,0:06:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,在婴儿开始行走之前 \N{\rEN}before the baby starts walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.12,0:06:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我要在游泳池周围竖起围栏\N{\rEN}And I get to put up a fence around the pool
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在婴儿开始行走之前 \N{\rEN}before the baby starts walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.83,0:06:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,, - 谢谢  - 不客气 \N{\rEN}- Thank you. - You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.16,0:06:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 在我忘记之前 你们有没有看到我的露营刀？\N{\rEN}Hey, before I forget, have either of you seen my camping knife?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.16,0:06:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 那个有雕刻把手的黑色的？\N{\rEN}You know, the black one with the carved handle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:29.87,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我会留意的  - 谢谢 公主 \N{\rEN}- I'll keep an eye out. - Gracias, princesa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.51,0:06:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 \N{\rEN}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.00,0:06:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,享受 享受！吃你的煎饼 \N{\rEN}Enjoy, enjoy! Eat your pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.63,0:06:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\rEN}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 凯德怎么了？\N{\rEN}Emma, what's wrong with Cade?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.48,0:06:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他扔了勺子 洗碗机里就会有新的 \N{\rEN}If he threw his spoon, there's some new ones in the dishwasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.68,0:07:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,, - 这是什么？ - 罗伯想和你谈谈这件事 \N{\rEN}- What's this? - Rob wanted to talk to you about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他过去常在那里讲课 他说这太神奇了 \N{\rEN}He used to lecture there. He said it's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,95%的毕业生就读常春藤 \N{\rEN}95% of their graduates go Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.60,0:07:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,, - 既然我知道你在看耶鲁… - 这是寄宿学校吗？\N{\rEN}- Since I know you're looking at Yale... - Is it a boarding school?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.87,0:07:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不是那样 离这里只有几个小时的路程 \N{\rEN}No, no. Not like that. It's only a couple hours away,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这样你周末就可以回家了 \N{\rEN}so you could come home on the weekends.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下！\N{\rEN}Just a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.36,0:07:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,, - 这是罗伯的主意？ - 他只想要对你最好的东西 \N{\rEN}- This was Rob's idea? - He just wants what's best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何 这只是需要考虑的事情 \N{\rEN}Anyways, it's just something to think about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.80,0:07:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,, - 祝你今天好运 玩得开心  - 谢谢 孩子 我需要这个 \N{\rEN}- Good luck today. Have fun. - Thanks, kiddo. I needed that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,, - 斯蒂芬 你看起来真可爱  - 真正地\N{\rEN}- Steph, you look so cute. - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.07,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直在告诉你 这是装饰品 对吧 Em？\N{\rEN}I keep telling you. It's adorbs. Right, Em?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,, - 是的 它真的很适合你  - 你不觉得太短吗？\N{\rEN}- Yeah. It really suits you. - You don't think it's too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.72,0:08:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不你在开玩笑吧？你看起来很棒 \N{\rEN}No! Are you kidding me? You look amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.87,0:08:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,, - 看起来很棒  - 非常感谢 \N{\rEN}- It looks great. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧第二定律 \N{\rEN}All right. Second Law.
