Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.24,0:09:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你好他们把你移到我旁边 \N{\rEN}Hello! They moved you next to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我很幸运 \N{\rEN}I know. Lucky me.
