Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,一篮子吻   \N{\rEN}A basket of kisses...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.64,0:21:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,, - 嗯？艾玛 怎么了？ - 没有什么只是累了 \N{\rEN}- Em? Emma, what's wrong? - Nothing. Just tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.24,0:21:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,, - 苏普？我能加入你们吗？ - 是的 绝对 \N{\rEN}- S'up? Can I join you guys? - Yeah, absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.27,0:21:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,, - 到目前为止 你觉得这里怎么样？ - 我哪里都不喜欢 \N{\rEN}- So, how do you like it here so far? - I don't like it anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.24,0:21:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你不能在这里抽烟  - 不\N{\rEN}- You can't smoke in here. - No?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.55,0:21:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,, - 那你是从哪里转过来的？ - 圣奥尔登酒店 \N{\rEN}- So where'd you transfer from? - St. Alden's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的上帝！所以你们两个认识吗？\N{\rEN}My God! So you two, like, know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.27,0:22:03.27,Default,,0,0,0,,伊什 我当时叫凯蒂 \N{\rEN}Ish. I went by Katie back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你应该说点什么 \N{\rEN}You should've said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.35,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得你很聪明 你最终会明白的 \N{\rEN}You think you're smart. You would've figured it out eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.44,0:22:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,, - 或者不是  - 所以等等 \N{\rEN}- Or not. - So wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.35,0:22:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识那个溺水的孩子吗？\N{\rEN}You knew that kid who drowned?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,, - 那个老师呢？ - 是 啊\N{\rEN}- And that teacher? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起你爸爸的事 \N{\rEN}Sorry about your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的 \N{\rEN}It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.35,0:22:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我想… - 你应该问问她 \N{\rEN}- I think... - You should ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我明天要在我家开一个睡衣派对 \N{\rEN}I'm having a slumber party at my place tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.11,0:22:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这更像是一个舞蹈队的事情 但你完全应该来 \N{\rEN}It's more of a dance team thing, but you should totally come.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,大概\N{\rEN}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.03,0:22:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,再见 艾玛 \N{\rEN}See ya around, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.75,0:22:55.40,Default,,0,0,0,,听起来不错 \N{\rEN}That sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.96,0:22:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,和这是给你的 \N{\rEN}And... this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.24,0:23:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢 \N{\rEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.55,0:23:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,德纳达 \N{\rEN}De nada.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.83,0:23:07.63,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你知道吗… - 这听起来像是大便般的叫声 \N{\rEN}- You know what... - That sounds like a poopy cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.64,0:23:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,, - 放开我！ - 不 我明白了 让我   \N{\rEN}- Let me go! - No. I got it. Let me just...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.83,0:23:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你确定吗？ - 这样做 \N{\rEN}- Are you sure? - do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.07,0:23:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你能看这个吗？ - 我会看的 \N{\rEN}- Can you watch this? - I will watch this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我马上回来  - 我会尽力的 \N{\rEN}- I'll be right back. - I'll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.35,0:23:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,, - 那是你的手机吗？ - 该死 在办公室里 \N{\rEN}- Is that your phone? - Darn it. It's in the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.00,0:23:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可以你看这些 我两分钟 \N{\rEN}Okay... you watch these, I'll be two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.20,0:23:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\rEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.96,0:23:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEN}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.44,0:23:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 是的 我们肯定还有十分钟 \N{\rEN}Hey, yes. We're definitely still on for ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.64,0:23:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 一切都干净 \N{\rEN}Okay, all clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.31,0:23:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很干净 好孩子 \N{\rEN}All clean. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.03,0:23:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特？\N{\rEN}Robert?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.31,0:24:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧\N{\rEN}Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.68,0:24:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特！\N{\rEN}Robert!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.96,0:24:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,灭火器   它在水槽下面！\N{\rEN}The fire extinguisher... it's under the sink!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:12.83,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 不 不要 \N{\rEN}Emma, no, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.27,0:24:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为你应该在看 \N{\rEN}I thought you were supposed to be watching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.92,0:24:22.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我在看 我不知道发生了什么 我把它留给艾玛了 \N{\rEN}I was watching it. I don't know what happened. I left it with Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.44,0:24:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我不得不去洗手间 我离开了两秒钟 \N{\rEN}I had to go to the bathroom. I was gone for two seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.27,0:24:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,, - 这不是我的错！ - 那是谁的错？\N{\rEN}- It's not my fault! - Well, then whose fault is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.24,0:24:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 请安静 你们两个 \N{\rEN}Okay, quiet, please, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.35,0:24:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我们应该再做一次外卖吗？ - 外卖很好 \N{\rEN}- Should we do takeout again? - Takeout's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.03,0:24:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 无论你说话与否 成本都是一样的 \N{\rEN}You know, it costs the same whether you talk or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.11,0:24:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 \N{\rEN}I'm aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.92,0:24:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你的脑子里到底在想什么？\N{\rEN}What is running through that brain of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.92,0:24:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果物理定律也适用于人呢？\N{\rEN}What if the laws of physics applied to people as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.27,0:24:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,行动相等和相反的反应？\N{\rEN}Action. Equal and opposite reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.03,0:25:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这不是牛顿的意思 \N{\rEN}I don't think that's what Newton meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.68,0:25:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我阿姨想送我去寄宿学校 \N{\rEN}My aunt wants to send me to a boarding school.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.88,0:25:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 为了记录在案 我听说学校很优秀 \N{\rEN}I'm aware. And just for the record, I've heard that school is outstanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.51,0:25:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,, - 它的校友最终在全国各地的常春藤盟校毕业 \N{\rEN}- Its alumni end up at... - Ivy Leagues all across the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.11,0:25:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道 我已经看过小册子了 两次\N{\rEN}I'm aware. I've read the brochure. Twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.92,0:25:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大多数穿你鞋子的女孩都会很兴奋 \N{\rEN}Most girls in your shoes would be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.44,0:25:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,, - 罗伯特要我离开房子  - 他为什么要这样？\N{\rEN}- Robert wants me out of the house. - And why would he want that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,你的行为是否会促使他做出决定？\N{\rEN}Did you behave in such a way that might have precipitated his decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.03,0:25:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,你的行为引起了反应吗？\N{\rEN}Did your action cause a reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.31,0:25:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,, - 也许吧  - 所以你制造了一个问题 \N{\rEN}- Maybe. - So you created a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.75,0:25:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对于我们自己制造的问题 正确的反应是什么？\N{\rEN}And what is the proper response to a problem of our own making?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.96,0:25:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,解决问题 \N{\rEN}Solving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.64,0:25:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你擅长解决问题 是吗？\N{\rEN}And you are good at solving problems, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.44,0:25:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,对我很擅长解决问题 \N{\rEN}Yes. I'm very good at solving problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.35,0:26:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 马奇博士 这非常有帮助 \N{\rEN}Thank you, Dr. March. This has been incredibly helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.07,0:26:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我很高兴能够帮助你 艾玛 \N{\rEN}I am so glad to have been able to help you, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.75,0:26:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧再见\N{\rEN}All right. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.79,0:26:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特 我想道歉   \N{\rEN}Robert, I wanted to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.00,0:26:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特叔叔 我只是想道歉   \N{\rEN}Uncle Robert, I just wanted to apologize...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.07,0:26:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEN}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.31,0:26:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,, - 嘿  - 我以为你可能渴了 \N{\rEN}- Hey. - I thought you might be thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.00,0:26:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能谈谈吗？\N{\rEN}Can we talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.59,0:26:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特叔叔 我只是想道歉\N{\rEN}Uncle Robert, I just wanted to apologize
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.44,0:26:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为忘了把刀还给你 \N{\rEN}for forgetting to give you back your knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.88,0:26:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在所有泳池设备旁边找到了它\N{\rEN}I found it next to all the pool equipment
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.03,0:26:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我忘了把它还给你 所以   \N{\rEN}and it just slipped my mind to give it back to you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.11,0:26:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 \N{\rEN}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.31,0:27:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢 \N{\rEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.72,0:27:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 每个人都很难改变 \N{\rEN}You know, change is hard for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.44,0:27:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说 在我爸爸之后 \N{\rEN}For me, after my dad, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.48,0:27:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,只是   我想 有时候 我脑子里有东西   \N{\rEN}it's just... I guess, sometimes, something gets in my head and...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.00,0:27:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我会做一些我不该做的事 \N{\rEN}maybe I'll do something I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.72,0:27:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解 \N{\rEN}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.64,0:27:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也许这对我们有好处？也许我们可以重新开始 \N{\rEN}Maybe this is good for us? Maybe we could start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.72,0:27:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,是 啊\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.20,0:27:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 也许圣克里斯平对我有好处 \N{\rEN}And who knows, maybe St. Crispin's will be good for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.51,0:27:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,, - 真的吗？ - 是 啊90%的毕业生就读常春藤 \N{\rEN}- Really? - Yeah. 90% of their grads go Ivy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.59,0:27:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我想去常春藤 所以我想说这很有可能 \N{\rEN}I want to go Ivy, so I'd say those are pretty good odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.88,0:27:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,是 啊\N{\rEN}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.00,0:27:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,此外 你在做对你的家人和我最有利的事 所以 \N{\rEN}Besides, you're doing what's best for your family and for me, so.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.11,0:27:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,非常感谢 \N{\rEN}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.16,0:27:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不客气 \N{\rEN}You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.44,0:27:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 \N{\rEN}Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.48,0:27:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 你想搭车去派对吗？\N{\rEN}Emma, do you want a ride to the party?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.59,0:28:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不 斯蒂芬斯就在拐角处 我要走了 \N{\rEN}No, Steph's is right around the corner. I'm going to walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.51,0:28:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可以好吧 玩得开心！如果你需要什么 请告诉我 什么都可以 \N{\rEN}Okay. Well, have fun! Just let me know if you need anything. Anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.64,0:28:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我会的  - 和\N{\rEN}- I will. - And...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.64,0:28:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特告诉我你们俩很好 \N{\rEN}Robert told me you two are good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.68,0:28:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不知道这让我有多开心 亲爱的熊 \N{\rEN}You have no idea how happy that makes me, honey bear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.51,0:28:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛？\N{\rEN}Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.31,0:28:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉？\N{\rEN}Angela?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.96,0:29:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,进来吧\N{\rEN}Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.27,0:29:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,, - 嗨！ - 你好\N{\rEN}- Hi! - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.20,0:29:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 请坐 \N{\rEN}Come on. Go have a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.64,0:29:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,, - 这不是很好笑吗？ - 真是太搞笑了 \N{\rEN}- Isn't that hilarious? - That's so hilarious.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.51,0:29:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们得到了什么？\N{\rEN}What did you guys get?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.24,0:29:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我想是的 - 我就是这么说的 \N{\rEN}- I think so. - That's what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.68,0:29:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那是谁？\N{\rEN}Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.83,0:29:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,, - 是凯特 - 对 \N{\rEN}- It's Kat. - Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.83,0:29:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是不明白你们为什么要邀请她 \N{\rEN}I still don't see why you guys had to invite her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.31,0:29:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她是你的朋友 我想表现得很好 \N{\rEN}Because she's your friend. I was trying to be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.27,0:30:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴有一些女孩在这里 \N{\rEN}It is so nice to have some of the girls on the team here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.79,0:30:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 你们女孩玩得很开心 记住 \N{\rEN}Now, you girls have fun. And remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.96,0:30:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你真正与之竞争的人只有你自己 \N{\rEN}the only person you're ever really competing with is yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.55,0:30:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,, - 谢谢 妈妈  - 这真的很有帮助 \N{\rEN}- Thanks, Mom. - That's really helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.75,0:30:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你和艾玛以前认识有多酷？\N{\rEN}So how cool is it that you and Emma used to know each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.59,0:30:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,不过 我们并不是真正的朋友 \N{\rEN}We weren't really friends, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.16,0:30:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有？\N{\rEN}We weren't?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.44,0:30:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 让我们面对现实吧 你和任何人都不是真正的朋友 \N{\rEN}I mean, let's face it. You weren't really friends with anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.64,0:30:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我肯定那不是真的  - 确实如此 \N{\rEN}- I'm sure that's not true. - It so is.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.64,0:30:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,还记得那次我绊倒了 你偷了我的手表吗？\N{\rEN}Remember that time I tripped and you stole my watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.88,0:30:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我不认为那是我 \N{\rEN}- I don't think that was me. - It was.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.68,0:30:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但不管怎样 很酷 \N{\rEN}But whatever. It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.75,0:30:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有人想玩游戏吗？\N{\rEN}Anyone wanna play a game?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.20,0:30:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,对\N{\rEN}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.11,0:31:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特？\N{\rEN}Robert?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.59,0:31:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特？\N{\rEN}Robert?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.24,0:31:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可以既然这是我的房子 我能先走吗？\N{\rEN}Okay. Do I get to go first since it's my house?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.40,0:31:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有在考试中作弊过 \N{\rEN}Never have I ever cheated on a test.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.35,0:31:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天 我的天 \N{\rEN}My god. My god.
