Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.03,0:42:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道 我想这是我的“演讲” \N{\rEN}I don't know, I guess that's my "speech".
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.88,0:42:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,请投票给我当舞蹈队长 \N{\rEN}Please vote for me as dance captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.11,0:42:24.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你不这么做 我想 \N{\rEN}If you don't, no hard feelings, I guess,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.71,0:42:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 走吧 黄蜂！\N{\rEN}and, yeah, go, Wasps!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.48,0:42:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 下一个是谁？\N{\rEN}Okay, who's up next?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.00,0:42:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEN}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.51,0:42:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,好消息 罗伯特一周后就能回家 \N{\rEN}Good news. Robert gets to come home in one week.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.23,0:42:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我只需要为他整理一下这个房间 \N{\rEN}I just have to sort out this room for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.48,0:42:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,, - 因为他的轮椅  - 太好了 \N{\rEN}- Because of his wheelchair. - That's great.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.80,0:42:52.91,Default,,0,0,0,,这个周末你将接受圣克里斯平的采访 \N{\rEN}And you have an interview with St. Crispin's this weekend.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.92,0:42:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,他们只是想和你打交道\N{\rEN}They just want to touch base with you
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.67,0:42:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,看看你对入学的感觉 好吗？\N{\rEN}and see how you're feeling about enrollment, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.28,0:42:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我等不及了 \N{\rEN}I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.23,0:43:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,进展如何？\N{\rEN}How did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.28,0:43:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芬赢了 我真为她高兴 \N{\rEN}Steph won. I am so happy for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.67,0:43:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,, - 艾玛 你想谈谈吗？ - 不 不 我没有 很抱歉打扰一下\N{\rEN}- Emma, do you want to talk about it? - No. No, I don't. Sorry. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.36,0:43:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 \N{\rEN}Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.23,0:43:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里 \N{\rEN}Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.63,0:43:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 我有多年的经验 \N{\rEN}Don't you worry, I've got many years' experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.40,0:43:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 \N{\rEN}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.23,0:44:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这里很好 杰出的\N{\rEN}That's good here. Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.84,0:44:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为家里有一个青少年 \N{\rEN}Since there is a teen in the household,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.88,0:44:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,药柜必须始终上锁 \N{\rEN}the medicine cabinet must remain locked at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.96,0:44:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,随身携带一把钥匙 随身携带 我也会随身携带 \N{\rEN}Take one key and keep it on your person, always, and I'll have mine as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.32,0:44:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\rEN}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.03,0:44:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 嘿\N{\rEN}Emma. Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.67,0:44:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,进来 公主 不要害羞 \N{\rEN}Come in, princesa. Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.11,0:44:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我侄女艾玛 艾玛 这是科拉 \N{\rEN}My niece, Emma. Emma, this is Cora.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.23,0:44:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她将在白天和我们一起帮助罗伯特 \N{\rEN}She's going to be with us during the day to help out with Robert.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.71,0:44:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,, - 嗨  - 你好\N{\rEN}- Hi. - Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.96,0:44:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要什么 请告诉我 \N{\rEN}If you ever need anything, just let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.07,0:44:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我在考虑像我阿姨一样去医学院 \N{\rEN}I'm thinking about going into medicine like my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.51,0:44:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,杰出的你应该如此骄傲 \N{\rEN}Excellent. You should be so proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.44,0:44:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEN}Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.59,0:44:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,很高兴你回到家里 \N{\rEN}It's nice to have you back inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.44,0:44:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,回家真好 \N{\rEN}It's so good to be home.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.55,0:44:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你感觉怎么样？\N{\rEN}How do you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.48,0:44:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,非常非常糟糕 \N{\rEN}Very, very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.40,0:44:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,20分钟后服用止痛药 \N{\rEN}Pain meds in 20 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.11,0:45:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在很痛苦 \N{\rEN}I'm in so much pain right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.63,0:45:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 重点是让你被淘汰 而不是让你上钩 \N{\rEN}Yeah, the point is to get you weened off, not get you hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.32,0:45:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,正确的你能告诉我我的臀部和腿吗？\N{\rEN}Right. Can you tell that to my hips and my legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.67,0:45:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,, - 罗伯特… - 我很好 \N{\rEN}- Robert... - I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.51,0:45:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得发生了什么吗？\N{\rEN}Do you remember what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.23,0:45:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\rEN}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.07,0:45:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,纳达 只是\N{\rEN}Nada. Just...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.07,0:45:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,黑色\N{\rEN}black.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.36,0:45:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,, - 卫生间？ - 是 啊让我给你看 \N{\rEN}- Restroom? - Yeah. Let me show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.44,0:45:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你渴吗？\N{\rEN}Are you thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.07,0:45:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里\N{\rEN}Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.67,0:45:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.32,0:45:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么\N{\rEN}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.63,0:45:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你带来了这个 \N{\rEN}I brought you this.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.32,0:45:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这样 你总能感觉到他很亲近 \N{\rEN}That way, you can always feel close to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.84,0:45:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,真周到 艾玛 非常感谢 \N{\rEN}That's very thoughtful, Emma. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.55,0:46:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我在努力坚持下去 就像我能坚持多久一样 \N{\rEN}I'm trying to stick at it, like, as long as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.19,0:46:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你能给我们一秒钟吗？ - 是的 当然 绝对地\N{\rEN}- Think you could give us a second? - Yeah, sure. Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.55,0:46:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我会在课堂上和你见面  - 可以再见\N{\rEN}- I'll just meet you in class. - Okay. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.36,0:46:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,, - 什么？你想要什么？ - 那就是现在的情况？六\N{\rEN}- What? What do you want? - So that's what now? Six?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.32,0:46:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,, - 六个什么？ - 六个不幸的巧合 \N{\rEN}- Six what? - Six unfortunate coincidences.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.92,0:46:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但最后一个并没有按照你想要的方式进行 是吗？\N{\rEN}But the last one didn't really work out the way you wanted it to, did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.40,0:46:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芬还是打败了你 我知道你的一切 \N{\rEN}Steph still beat you. I know all about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.55,0:46:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,, - 告诉我  - 我应该从哪里开始？\N{\rEN}- Do tell. - Where should I start?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.44,0:46:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,管家从楼梯上摔下来？米洛溺水了？\N{\rEN}With the housekeeper falling down the stairs? Milo drowning?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.23,0:46:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,埃利斯太太的车祸？一个保姆被烧死？\N{\rEN}Mrs. Ellis' car wreck? A babysitter burning to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.11,0:46:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,一个父亲中枪了 一个继父被汽车碾压 \N{\rEN}A dad getting shot. A stepuncle getting crushed by a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.80,0:46:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在一只狗在公园里被砍了？\N{\rEN}And now a dog getting chopped up in a park?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.44,0:46:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,, - 巧合？还是模式？ - Stray Kat有爪子 \N{\rEN}- Coincidences? Or a pattern? - Stray Kat has claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.84,0:46:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直很忙 \N{\rEN}You've been busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.28,0:46:52.67,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我真的那么忙 你可能需要小心 \N{\rEN}If I've really been that busy, you might want to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.67,0:46:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还是怎样\N{\rEN}Or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.11,0:46:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我会告诉大家的  - 告诉他们什么？\N{\rEN}- I'll tell everyone. - Tell them what?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.71,0:46:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真相！\N{\rEN}The truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.88,0:46:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛？\N{\rEN}Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.63,0:47:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你要来吗？ - 我马上就到 \N{\rEN}- Are you coming? - I'll be there in a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.63,0:47:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,事故总是发生在人们身上 \N{\rEN}Accidents happen all the time to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.44,0:47:10.75,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是像你这样的人 \N{\rEN}Especially people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.76,0:47:12.63,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这样的人？\N{\rEN}People like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.76,0:47:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,伤害自己的人 \N{\rEN}People who hurt themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.63,0:47:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能伤害了自己 但我真的为你感到难过 \N{\rEN}I may have hurt myself, but it's really you I feel sorry for.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:25.03,0:47:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 你不应该担心我 笨蛋 \N{\rEN}Well, you shouldn't worry about me, silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.92,0:47:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我为你感到难过 \N{\rEN}I feel bad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.44,0:47:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你将永远孤独 \N{\rEN}You'll always be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.00,0:47:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,大概\N{\rEN}Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.51,0:47:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,但至少我不会是你 凯蒂凯特 \N{\rEN}But at least I won't be you, Kitty Kat.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.80,0:47:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是认真的吗？\N{\rEN}Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.03,0:47:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能只是打人 你到底怎么了？你没事吧？\N{\rEN}You can't just slap people. What the hell's wrong with you? You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.67,0:47:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,她疯了！\N{\rEN}She's insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.15,0:47:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,, - 这是怎么回事！ - 她扇了她一巴掌 \N{\rEN}- What's going on here! - She slapped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.63,0:47:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,, - 她扇了我一巴掌！ - 没有什么\N{\rEN}- She slapped me! - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.96,0:47:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,凯特 那是拘留 \N{\rEN}Kat. That's detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.84,0:47:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开！\N{\rEN}Piss off!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.19,0:48:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,, - 一个星期！ - 无论什么\N{\rEN}- For a week! - Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.96,0:48:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我勒个去？\N{\rEN}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.19,0:48:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,内森 请带她去护士办公室 \N{\rEN}Nathan, please take her to the nurse's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.44,0:48:05.96,Default,,0,0,0,,当然来吧\N{\rEN}Of course. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.80,0:48:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么不在剩下的时间里放松一下？\N{\rEN}Why don't you just relax for the rest of the period?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.15,0:48:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你需要什么 请告诉我 \N{\rEN}Let me know if you need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.51,0:49:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,, - 嘿 是什么 蜜熊？ - 没有什么\N{\rEN}- Hey. What is it, honeybear? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.71,0:49:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 来吧 \N{\rEN}Emma, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.67,0:49:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是我 \N{\rEN}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.88,0:49:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我明白了 这是一个艰难的几个星期 但   \N{\rEN}All right, I get it, it's been a rough couple of weeks, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.76,0:49:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 学校怎么样？\N{\rEN}I mean, how's school?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.67,0:49:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,, - 没事的  - 可以\N{\rEN}- It's okay. - Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.88,0:49:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,有个女孩 她的名字是凯特 \N{\rEN}There's this girl. Her name is Kat.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.55,0:49:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她从圣奥尔登转学 \N{\rEN}She transferred from St. Alden's.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.03,0:49:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你认识她吗？她和你同年级吗？\N{\rEN}Did you know her? Was she in the same grade as you?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.48,0:49:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不是真的 \N{\rEN}Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.80,0:49:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,她最近刚刚对我说了一些非常糟糕的话 \N{\rEN}She's just been saying some really awful things to me lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.51,0:49:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,关于\N{\rEN}About?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.00,0:49:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,关于米洛 \N{\rEN}About Milo.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.63,0:49:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,埃利斯夫人 我爸爸 \N{\rEN}Mrs. Ellis. My dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:56.32,0:49:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 她认为我和这事有关系 \N{\rEN}You know, she thinks I had something to do with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.03,0:50:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,发生在我们身上的一切 \N{\rEN}everything that happened to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.76,0:50:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都不想说 但她今天打了我 \N{\rEN}I wasn't going to say anything, but she hit me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.11,0:50:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:08.92,0:50:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 最近发生的一切 \N{\rEN}Yeah, and just with everything that's been going on lately,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.23,0:50:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 这太可怕了 \N{\rEN}I mean, it's just awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:13.71,0:50:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我向你保证 我会很快就把这件事搞定 可以\N{\rEN}I promise you, I am going to squash this real quick. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.84,0:50:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我早上第一件事就是打电话 \N{\rEN}I'm going to make a phone call first thing in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.63,0:50:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,过来 没关系 \N{\rEN}Come here. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.15,0:50:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是一个粗糙的补丁 孩子 \N{\rEN}This is just a rough patch, kiddo.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.23,0:50:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会挺过去的 我保证 \N{\rEN}We are going to get through this. I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.80,0:50:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿 没关系 \N{\rEN}Hey, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.32,0:50:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,所以有   有什么好消息吗？\N{\rEN}So is there... any good news?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.51,0:50:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我是说 有个男孩… - 真正地\N{\rEN}- I mean, there's this boy... - Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.92,0:50:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他很可爱 \N{\rEN}He's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.15,0:50:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉\N{\rEN}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.07,0:51:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我不想听你调查 \N{\rEN}No. I don't want to hear that you'll look into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.63,0:51:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望它立即得到处理 \N{\rEN}I want it taken care of immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.23,0:51:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,对如果你不打算给凯特的父母打电话 我会的 \N{\rEN}Yes. And if you don't plan on calling Kat's parents, then I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.40,0:51:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,可以好吧 非常感谢 \N{\rEN}Okay. All right then. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:15.48,0:51:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,, - 还有好消息吗？ - 我希望如此 \N{\rEN}- More good news, I take it? - I wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.55,0:51:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芬怎么样？\N{\rEN}How's Steph?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.88,0:51:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她好了一点 因为震动已经过去了 \N{\rEN}She a bit better, now that the shock has worn off.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.11,0:51:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哈罗德答应今年夏天给她买一只新狗 \N{\rEN}Harold promised to buy her a new dog this summer.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.11,0:51:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还没弄清楚是谁干的？\N{\rEN}They still haven't figured out who did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.11,0:51:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 一个慢跑者看到有人在遛狗 \N{\rEN}No. No. A jogger saw someone walking the dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:32.11,0:51:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的安全摄像头上有一点 但没有确定 \N{\rEN}We got a little on our security cam, but nothing determinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.07,0:51:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,谁做那样的事？\N{\rEN}Who does something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.48,0:51:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会杀死一只无辜的动物？\N{\rEN}Who would kill an innocent animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.51,0:51:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,哈罗德觉得我疯了 \N{\rEN}Harold thinks I'm crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.00,0:51:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,但我可以发誓 那个镜头里是一个年轻的女人 \N{\rEN}but I could have sworn that it was young woman in that footage.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.28,0:51:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我会寄给你的  - 是 啊\N{\rEN}- I'll send it to you. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.44,0:51:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是告诉艾玛祝贺舞蹈队队长 \N{\rEN}But... tell Emma congratulations on back-up Dance Team Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.07,0:51:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芬说她对此很甜蜜 \N{\rEN}Steph said she was very sweet about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.59,0:51:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我会让她知道的 \N{\rEN}I will let her know.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.96,0:52:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,斯蒂芬！\N{\rEN}Steph!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.88,0:52:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,快来找护士！我的天！\N{\rEN}Someone get the nurse! My god!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.96,0:52:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拨打911！她需要吃药 \N{\rEN}Call 911! She needs her meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.92,0:52:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,, - 斯蒂芬妮！ - 我的天！\N{\rEN}- Stephanie! - My god!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.63,0:52:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,, - 这非常令人失望  - 是什么？\N{\rEN}- This is very disappointing. - What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.00,0:52:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你继续骚扰艾玛·格罗斯曼 \N{\rEN}Your continued harassment of Emma Grossman.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.80,0:52:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不容忍学校的暴力行为 \N{\rEN}We don't condone violence at the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:50.88,0:52:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 听着 这不是我的错 \N{\rEN}Okay, listen, it was not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.96,0:52:55.03,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我只是… - 斯蒂芬妮·洛福德癫痫发作了 \N{\rEN}- I was just... - Stephanie Lowford's had a seizure.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.03,0:52:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她的咪达唑仑不见了 我打了911 他们正在赶来 \N{\rEN}Her midazolam is missing. I've called 911 and they're on their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.48,0:53:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛   \N{\rEN}Emma...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.19,0:53:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的天 \N{\rEN}My god.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.15,0:53:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,, - 瑞秋 我… - 学校发生了什么事！\N{\rEN}- Rachel, I... - Something happened at the school!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.88,0:53:52.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什么？\N{\rEN}What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.84,0:53:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没有什么\N{\rEN}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:57.71,0:54:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你不会对我撒谎吧？ - 不 我永远不会 \N{\rEN}- You wouldn't lie to me, would you? - No. I would never.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:02.36,0:54:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我没生气 艾玛 我不是 我只需要知道真相 \N{\rEN}I'm not mad, Emma. I'm not. I just need to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.36,0:54:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,, - 关于？ - 每件事\N{\rEN}- About? - Everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.15,0:54:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你对你的朋友斯蒂芬妮做了什么吗？\N{\rEN}Did you do something to your friend, Stephanie?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:13.11,0:54:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,她癫痫发作了 这怎么可能是我的错？\N{\rEN}She had a seizure. How could that have been my fault?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.51,0:54:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,, - 她的狗？ - 那不是我 \N{\rEN}- Her dog? - That wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.32,0:54:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 我看见你了 我在环形门摄像头上看到你了 \N{\rEN}Emma, I saw you. I saw you on the ring-door cam.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.59,0:54:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,, - 不 你没有！ - 是的 艾玛 这是你的毛衣 \N{\rEN}- No, you didn't! - I did, Emma. This is your sweater.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:26.71,0:54:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,, - 不 别骗我了！ - 告诉我真相！\N{\rEN}- No. Stop lying to me! - Tell me the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.80,0:54:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,, - 艾玛 告诉我！ - 好吧 对不起！\N{\rEN}- Emma, tell me! - Okay, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.59,0:54:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧我让她的狗出来了 好吗？\N{\rEN}All right? I let her dog out, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.19,0:54:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我很想当舞蹈队长 斯蒂芬妮 她只是   \N{\rEN}I wanted to be Dance Captain so bad, and Stephanie, she just...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.71,0:54:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,她让我很生气 \N{\rEN}she makes me so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.44,0:54:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我只是   我想   \N{\rEN}So I just... I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.80,0:54:45.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我想伤害她 我把她的狗放了出来 \N{\rEN}I wanted to hurt her and I let her dog out.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.15,0:54:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我以为它会回来 我以为他们会找到的 对不起！\N{\rEN}I thought it was going to come back. I thought they would find it. I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.03,0:54:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证！我保证我没有伤害它！我发誓！\N{\rEN}I promise! I promise I didn't hurt it! I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:50.59,0:54:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,好的 好的 可以没关系 \N{\rEN}Okay, okay. Okay. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.71,0:54:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝没关系 \N{\rEN}God. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.76,0:55:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉阿姨 你能给我一篮子拥抱吗？\N{\rEN}What would you give me for a basket of hugs, Aunt Angela?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.15,0:55:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那里\N{\rEN}There.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.32,0:56:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,现在 看到了吗？这没那么糟 \N{\rEN}Now, see? This isn't so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.96,0:56:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,有点冷 \N{\rEN}A little cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:04.71,0:56:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,57度 \N{\rEN}It's 57 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:07.63,0:56:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,新鲜空气能增强免疫系统 \N{\rEN}Fresh air builds the immune system.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.28,0:56:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道 在俄罗斯 他们曾经把孩子捆绑在一起\N{\rEN}You know, in Russia, they used to bundle up children
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.92,0:56:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,让他们在冬天的雪地里小睡一会儿 真实的故事 \N{\rEN}and have them take a nap in the snow in the winter. True story.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.80,0:56:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你想知道古巴人对俄罗斯人的看法吗？\N{\rEN}Do you want to know what Cubans think of the Russians?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:22.28,0:56:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我勒个去？\N{\rEN}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.19,0:56:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\rEN}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.88,0:56:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了\N{\rEN}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.48,0:57:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我需要帮忙  - 当然\N{\rEN}- I need a favor. - Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.15,0:57:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你能过一会儿把他带回来吗？\N{\rEN}Can you bring him back inside in a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.44,0:57:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我有一个小灾难要处理 \N{\rEN}I have a minor disaster to deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.15,0:57:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,, - 别担心 我明白了 - 好的 \N{\rEN}- Don't worry. I got it. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.07,0:57:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,, - 一切都好吗？ - 是的 很好 我已经处理好了 \N{\rEN}- Everything okay? - Yeah, it's good. I've got it handled.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.23,0:57:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿\N{\rEN}Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.44,0:57:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 嗨 内森 我是艾玛 \N{\rEN}Yeah, hi, Nathan. It's Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.23,0:57:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\N{\rEN}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.59,0:57:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 我什么都没做 \N{\rEN}No, I'm not doing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.03,0:57:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 我很好 外面很冷 \N{\rEN}Yeah, I'm good. It's quite chilly out.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.15,0:57:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛？\N{\rEN}Emma?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.84,0:58:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我想进去热身 吃药 \N{\rEN}I want to get inside and warm up, take my meds.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.23,0:58:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你能帮我进去吗？ - 无论什么\N{\rEN}- Can you help me in there? - Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.76,0:58:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛！\N{\rEN}Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.19,0:58:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 不 没什么 \N{\rEN}Yeah, no, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.84,0:58:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛！\N{\rEN}Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.15,0:58:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不 不 \N{\rEN}No, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.28,0:58:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我听过的最愚蠢的笑话 \N{\rEN}That's the stupidest joke I've ever heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.23,0:58:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,, - 是的  - 上帝\N{\rEN}- Yeah. - God.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.96,0:58:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,是 啊\N{\rEN}Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.28,0:58:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特？上帝的名义是什么？\N{\rEN}Robert? What in God's name?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.15,0:58:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,, - 罗伯特 你在干什么？ - 这里发生了什么？\N{\rEN}- Robert, what are you doing? - What is happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.36,0:58:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你不理我 我想… - 对不起 我刚打完电话 \N{\rEN}- You're ignoring me. I'm trying to... - I was finishing a call, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.51,0:59:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以自己做 看见\N{\rEN}I can do it myself. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.63,0:59:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,她回来接你 \N{\rEN}She was coming back to get you.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.15,0:59:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能再等几分钟吗？\N{\rEN}You couldn't have waited a few more minutes?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.48,0:59:08.76,Default,,0,0,0,, - 让我进去  - 好吧\N{\rEN}- Just get me inside. - All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.88,0:59:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那么…他叫什么名字？\N{\rEN}So... what's his name?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.80,0:59:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,内森 \N{\rEN}Nathan.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.11,0:59:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,内森   \N{\rEN}Nathan...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.32,0:59:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 我希望他没有这个那么固执 \N{\rEN}Well, I hope he's not as stubborn as this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.15,0:59:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,很抱歉这是剩菜 安吉拉一整天都在医院 \N{\rEN}Sorry. It's leftovers. Angela's been at the hospital all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.19,0:59:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经喂过凯德了 \N{\rEN}I already fed Cade.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.71,0:59:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望你早些时候没有生气 \N{\rEN}I hope you're not mad about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:51.51,0:59:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你愚弄了那么多人 \N{\rEN}You fool so many.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.40,0:59:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但不是我 \N{\rEN}But not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.07,0:59:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不再是了 \N{\rEN}Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.96,1:00:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么？\N{\rEN}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.67,1:00:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我记得一切 我知道是你干的 \N{\rEN}I remember everything. I know it was you.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.55,1:00:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你打算怎么办？ - 这就是我要做的 \N{\rEN}- What are you gonna do about it? - This is what I'm going to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.84,1:00:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱我的妻子 她也爱你 \N{\rEN}I love my wife, and she loves you,
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.28,1:00:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,所以伤害你会伤害她 我不想这样 \N{\rEN}so hurting you hurts her, and I don't want that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.15,1:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在她哥哥发生了什么事之后就没有了 \N{\rEN}Not after what happened to her brother.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.03,1:00:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 我会变得更好   \N{\rEN}So, I am going to get better...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.76,1:00:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也不说 \N{\rEN}and I'm not going to say anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.92,1:00:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,以换取什么？\N{\rEN}In exchange for what?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.96,1:00:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你将去寄宿学校 让孩子和我们独处 \N{\rEN}You will go to boarding school and leave the baby and us alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.88,1:00:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我不想做这两件事呢？\N{\rEN}What if I don't want to do either of those things?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.00,1:00:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 那我就说实话 \N{\rEN}Well, then I'm going to tell the truth.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.76,1:00:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉会受到伤害 但你会受到更多的伤害 \N{\rEN}And Angela will be hurt, but you will be hurt way more.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.55,1:00:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没有常春藤联盟 \N{\rEN}No Ivy League.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.55,1:00:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没有幸福的生活 什么都没有 \N{\rEN}No happy life. No nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.84,1:01:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你将永远被锁在外面 完全孤独 \N{\rEN}You will be locked away forever. Completely alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.67,1:01:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,妥协？\N{\rEN}Comprende?
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.88,1:01:10.36,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂奥 整个克拉克 \N{\rEN}Tio, entiendo claramente.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.00,1:01:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,对话的问题 \N{\rEN}Que bueno que tuvimos esta conversación.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.07,1:01:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,米吉塔 这是一个奇迹 \N{\rEN}Te tengo en la mira, mijita.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.03,1:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,, - 嘿  - 嘿\N{\rEN}- Hey. - Hey.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.96,1:02:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,, - 这是给谁的？ - 这是给你的 陪伴你 \N{\rEN}- Who's that for? - It's for you. To keep you company.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:54.92,1:02:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,, - 注意你  - 你要去哪里？\N{\rEN}- Keep an eye on you. - Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.44,1:02:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去拜访一位老朋友 \N{\rEN}I'm going to visit an old family friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.59,1:03:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,应该几个小时后回来 好吗？\N{\rEN}Should be back in a couple of hours, okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.51,1:03:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,, - 好的 凯德呢？ - 我要带着他 \N{\rEN}- Okay. What about Cade? - I'm taking him with me.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.40,1:03:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,, - 别担心 我很快就回来  - 没关系 你走吧 \N{\rEN}- Don't worry. I'll be back soon. - That's fine. You go.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.92,1:03:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,, - 尽情享受吧  - 可以\N{\rEN}- Enjoy yourself. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.00,1:03:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,, - 臀部怎么样？ - 它还在那里 \N{\rEN}- How's that hip? - It's still there.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.55,1:03:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,, - 它会痊愈的  - 可以\N{\rEN}- It'll heal. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.51,1:03:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我爱你  - 我也爱你 \N{\rEN}- I love you. - I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.03,1:03:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你准备好去兜风了吗？\N{\rEN}You ready to go for a car ride?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.40,1:03:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧 你会一直睡下去 对吧？\N{\rEN}Okay, you're going to sleep the whole way, right?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.51,1:03:37.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 好孩子 \N{\rEN}There we go. Good boy.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:38.15,1:03:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧 \N{\rEN}Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.48,1:04:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,布莱恩 你好\N{\rEN}Brian. Hi.
