Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.56,1:10:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,有人和我聊天真的很好 \N{\rEN}It's really nice to have someone to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:37.64,1:10:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我从来没有真正的人可以交谈 \N{\rEN}I never really have anyone to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,1:10:41.15,1:10:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,, - 不是真的  - 也许这是有原因的 \N{\rEN}- Not really. - Maybe there's a reason for that.
