Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.27,1:14:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,别惹精神病 \N{\rEN}Don't mess with psychos.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.35,1:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,真正地\N{\rEN}Really...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.60,1:14:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚才说了什么？\N{\rEN}What did I just say?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.68,1:14:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说 你想用这个做什么？\N{\rEN}I mean, what are you trying to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.23,1:14:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,上帝\N{\rEN}God.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.92,1:14:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,, - 现在你打算做什么？哭？ - 请\N{\rEN}- Now what are you going to do? Cry? - Please.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.35,1:14:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你不必这么做  - 你已经睡了 好吧\N{\rEN}- You don't have to do this. - Just go to sleep already. All right?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.60,1:14:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想这么说 但这有点无聊了 \N{\rEN}I hate to say it, but this is getting a little boring.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.39,1:14:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你对内森的建议 做我自己 \N{\rEN}Thank you for the advice about Nathan. Just be myself.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.96,1:14:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我会尝试的 \N{\rEN}I'll try.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.43,1:14:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,没有你 这是不可能的 \N{\rEN}This wouldn't have been possible without you.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.23,1:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的是我最好的朋友 \N{\rEN}You really are the best friend I've ever had.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.23,1:14:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛   \N{\rEN}Emma...
Dialogue: 0,1:15:11.68,1:15:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛？\N{\rEN}Emma?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.11,1:15:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉 你在家吗？\N{\rEN}Angela, are you home?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.43,1:15:28.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\rEN}Hello?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.72,1:15:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉？\N{\rEN}Angela?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.80,1:15:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛？\N{\rEN}Emma?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.07,1:16:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 伙计！\N{\rEN}I'm coming, buddy!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:14.23,1:16:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸来了 \N{\rEN}Daddy's coming.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.92,1:16:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是 啊我来了 伙计 \N{\rEN}Yeah. Here I come, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.56,1:16:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛？\N{\rEN}Emma?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.76,1:16:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,凯德！\N{\rEN}Cade!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:53.11,1:16:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸来了 伙计 \N{\rEN}Daddy's coming, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.88,1:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我来了 伙计 爸爸来了 \N{\rEN}I'm coming, buddy. Daddy's here.
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.15,1:17:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很好 \N{\rEN}Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.52,1:18:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛？\N{\rEN}Emma?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:05.07,1:18:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\N{\rEN}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:07.19,1:18:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,相等和相反的反应 \N{\rEN}Equal and opposite reactions.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.15,1:18:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,老实说 它可能总是以这种方式结束 \N{\rEN}To be honest, it was probably always going to end up this way.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.31,1:18:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 罗伯特 \N{\rEN}I am sorry, Robert.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.64,1:18:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,某种程度上 \N{\rEN}Sort of.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.47,1:18:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉 \N{\rEN}Angela.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.52,1:18:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛！\N{\rEN}Emma!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.43,1:18:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,, - 安吉拉阿姨！ - 艾玛！你做了什么？\N{\rEN}- Aunt Angela! - Emma! What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.27,1:18:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,, - 什么？ - 他对你的评价是对的！\N{\rEN}- What? - He was right about you!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.11,1:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,, - 你在说什么？ - 你爸爸 \N{\rEN}- What are you talking about? - Your dad.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:46.80,1:18:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我哥哥 他爱你胜过一切 但他是对的！\N{\rEN}My brother, he loved you more than anything, but he was right!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.39,1:18:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个怪物！\N{\rEN}You're a monster!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.35,1:18:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是那个意思！凯特只是想杀了我们！\N{\rEN}You don't mean that! Kat just tried to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.39,1:18:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,说谎者！你对她做了什么？\N{\rEN}Liar! What did you do to her?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:59.00,1:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,给罗伯特？你做了什么 艾玛？\N{\rEN}To Robert? What did you do, Emma?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.60,1:19:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,安吉拉！\N{\rEN}Angela!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.19,1:19:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,不……不要走 \N{\rEN}No... don't go.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.56,1:19:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特！\N{\rEN}Robert!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.23,1:19:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特！\N{\rEN}Robert!
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.23,1:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗨 朋友 \N{\rEN}Hi, friend.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.56,1:19:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特！\N{\rEN}Robert!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.64,1:20:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,罗伯特 醒醒 罗伯特 醒醒吧！\N{\rEN}Robert, wake up. Robert, wake up, please!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:06.52,1:20:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 快点 起来！\N{\rEN}Come on. Come on, get up!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:08.52,1:20:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,快点 我们得把你弄出去！\N{\rEN}Come on, we've got to get you out of here!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:12.64,1:20:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 罗伯特 请\N{\rEN}Come on, Robert. Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.76,1:20:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,帮助请\N{\rEN}Help! Please!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.27,1:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,请我阿姨！她还在里面！\N{\rEN}Please! My aunt! She's still in there!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.27,1:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这个女孩   她试图烧毁我们的房子 \N{\rEN}This girl... she tried to burn our house down.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:56.19,1:20:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,, - 求你了！你必须设法救她！ - 你在这里等着！\N{\rEN}- Please! You've got to try and save her! - You wait here!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.60,1:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛！你没事吧？\N{\rEN}Emma! Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.03,1:21:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,, - 我的天  - 耶稣基督 \N{\rEN}- My god. - Jesus Christ.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.15,1:21:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系 没关系 \N{\rEN}It's okay. It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.47,1:21:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是怎么发生的？\N{\rEN}How the hell did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.43,1:21:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系 没关系 \N{\rEN}It's okay. It's okay, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.96,1:21:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那么现在会发生什么呢？\N{\rEN}So what's going to happen now?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:33.00,1:21:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们有一个了不起的女人可以收留你\N{\rEN}We have an amazing woman who can take you in
Dialogue: 0,1:21:35.47,1:21:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,直到一切都整理好 \N{\rEN}until everything gets sorted.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.84,1:21:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉 艾玛 \N{\rEN}I'm so sorry, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.80,1:21:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我无法想象这对你来说有多困难 \N{\rEN}I can't imagine how difficult this is for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.31,1:21:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱我的阿姨 \N{\rEN}I loved my aunt.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.64,1:21:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还有我叔叔 \N{\rEN}And my uncle.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.07,1:21:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,凯德和我至少能在一起吗？\N{\rEN}Can Cade and I at least stay together?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.00,1:21:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会尽力的 \N{\rEN}We'll do our best.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:58.27,1:22:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,他是我唯一剩下的家人 \N{\rEN}He's the only family I have left.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:04.27,1:22:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要打几个电话 \N{\rEN}I need to make a few calls.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.72,1:22:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你需要什么吗？\N{\rEN}Is there anything you need?
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.96,1:22:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,艾玛 你知道这不是你的错 \N{\rEN}Emma, you know this isn't your fault.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.27,1:22:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会没事的 \N{\rEN}We'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.92,1:22:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是格罗斯曼 我们高高在上 \N{\rEN}We're Grossmans. We rise above.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.23,1:22:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可以\N{\rEN}Okay.
